  <summary date="2023-08-10T18:07:06Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Consumer Protection Remedies Act of 2022

This bill authorizes the Federal Trade Commission to seek, and courts to order, certain types of equitable relief such as restitution, contract rescission, and disgorgement in suits to enforce the laws within the commission's jurisdiction.</summary>
